metadata.name: active-win
metadata.author: Sindre Sorhus <sindresorhus@gmail.com> (https://sindresorhus.com)
metadata.description: Get metadata about the active window (title, id, bounds, owner, URL, etc)

metadata.name: better-sqlite3
metadata.author: Joshua Wise <joshuathomaswise@gmail.com>
metadata.description: The fastest and simplest library for SQLite in Node.js.

metadata.name: get-windows
metadata.author: Sindre Sorhus <sindresorhus@gmail.com> (https://sindresorhus.com)
metadata.description: Get metadata about the active window and open windows (title, id, bounds, owner, URL, etc)

metadata.name: node-notifier
metadata.author: Mikael Brevik
metadata.description: A Node.js module for sending notifications on native Mac, Windows (post and pre 8) and Linux (or Growl as fallback)
